snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Due to the availability of fake colours in the market, committee members chose not to celebrate Holi, which has left all of the Gokuldham society's members deeply upset and depressed. How come everyone chose to play Holi all of a sudden? What's the deal? Watch this incredibly fantastic Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Holi special episode to find out.


Show Name â€“ Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast â€“  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 1364
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #à¤¤à¤¾à¤°à¤•à¤®à¥‡à¤¹à¤¤à¤¾à¤•à¤¾à¤‰à¤²à¥à¤Ÿà¤¾à¤šà¤¶à¥à¤®à¤¾ #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Watch all the exciting clips of Holi Special: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1esHln9KXStCbSKq6ifX0a

snippet.title: Every Indian On Holi | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys 
Happy Holi ap sbko
This Holi Video has every Holi situation we experience. How we Indians celebrate holi . The crazy masti of Holi . Revenge wali holi , pyaar wali holi , dosto ke sath , holi fest ki holi , deciding holi songs playlist , board exams wali holi , holi during school exam , ipl wali holi , grooving on ap dhillon songs , enjoying bhang thandai , beer , gol gappe , dahi bhalle , gujia sweets , getting gifts from relatives gulal , rang , all the colors , pichkari , desi ghee gujia , hugging enemies sorting out the grudges , hitting with water balloons , water guns , dancing , enjoying holika dhayan , the festival of colors , Taking out revenge by applying colours, the foodies, getting painted first by the bf/gf, mixing pakka color into herbal colors, balloon horror created in society that we go through in holi days, and The Best Holi Fight between two groups.. Well you will love it and Relate with this video.. Enjoy and laugh out loud. 

This video is filled with  memories and situations we all have been in . 
Relish and Relive those fun moments
Do share it with your friends and family , Relatives , Neighbour  .. Comment down your Fav Part , 

HAPPY HOLI

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Shiddat Episode 13 [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Anmol Baloch - Digitally Presented by PEL - 25th March 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Shiddat Digitally Presented by PEL

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: Choli Ke Peeche | Crew - Kareena Kapoor K, @diljitdosanjh, Ila Arun, Alka Yagnik, Akshay & IP
snippet.description:
90s Ka Magic, Crew Ki Masti! Flying to you with a hot new track ft. Diljit Dosanjh.

"Choli Ke Peeche" is a High-Energy Song from the movie "Crew," featuring Tabu, Kareena Kapoor Khan, and Kriti Sanon. Sung by Diljit Dosanjh, Alka Yagnik, Ila Arun, and IP Singh, Music Recreated by Akshay & IP & Lyrics Penned By IP Singh

Crew In Cinemas On March29 

Stay updated with the latest videos from Tips Official, Subscribe on the below link.
http://youtube.com/tipsofficial

Song Details : 
Song - Choli Ke Peeche
Music Recreated by - Akshay & IP
Singers - Diljit Dosanjh, IP Singh, Alka Yagnik & Ila Arun
Lyrics - IP Singh
Music Arranged and Produced - Akshay Raheja & Abhishek Singh
Mix & Master -  Abhishek Ghatak

Original Credits - 
Original Film - Khal Nayak
Music - Laxmikant - Pyarelal
Singers - Alka Yagnik & Ila Arun
Lyrics - Anand Bakshi

Song Directed by - Farah Khan
Producers - Shobha Kapoor, Anil Kapoor, Ektaa R. Kapoor & Rhea Kapoor
Production House - Anil Kapoor Film And Communication Network Pvt Ltd. & Balaji Telefilms Ltd. 

Publicity Designers - Himanshu & Rahul Nanda
Visual Promotions - Feed The Wolf
Marketing Consultant - Aparna Desai

Movie Details : 
Banner: Balaji Telefilms, AKFC & Communication Network Production Pvt. Ltd
Starring Tabu, Kareena Kapoor Khan, Kriti Sanon, Diljit Dosanjh, and a special appearance by Kapil Sharma
Directed by Rajesh Krishnan
Produced by Shobha Kapoor & Anil Kapoor
Produced by Ektaa R. Kapoor & Rhea Kapoor
Music On Tips Industries Ltd.(Tips Music)

Lyrics:
Ku Ku Kuâ€¦ 
Jogiya Ve Mainu Aitthon Door Lae Ja Tu 
Seene Vich Dil Kare Dum Gutkoon 
Mundraan Pua(Pavaa) Ke Naale Majjhiyaan Chara Ke 
Mundraan Pua Ke Naale Majjhiyaan Chara Ke 
Keeta Jeenaan Mushkil Tu Mera 

Choli Ke Peeche Kya Hai 
Chunari Ke Niche Kya Hai 

Dass Mainu Gall Kudiye Tu Kitthon Aayi Ajj 
Jo Bhi Hai Choli Ke Peeche Mujhape Tu De Kharach 
Dekhoon Chhup Chhup Ke Main Tujhey Bolun Sach Sach 
Machne Lagi Tu Baby Too Much Too Much! 
Dekhiyo Na Gir Jaaye Dil Hai Meri 
Judna Ni Phir Haaye Dil Hai Mera 
Dekhiyo Na Gir Jaaye 
Dil Hai Meri Judna Ni Phir Haaye 
Dil Hai Mera Ye Dil Tu De De Apne Yaar Ko, Pyaar Ko.. 

Ku Ku Ku .. 
Resham Ka Lehenga Mera 
Resham Ka Lehenga 
Lehenga Hai Mehenga Mera 
Lehenga Hai Mehenga 
Lehenga Utha Ke Chaloon 
Ghoonghat Gira Ke Chaloon 
Kya Kya Bachaa Ke Chaloon
Raam Jiâ€¦ Raam Jiâ€¦
Oye Chori.. 

De Bata Tu Kya Hai Tere Seene Vich Na Mila Hai Tere Sa Zamaane Vich. 
Le Mujhey Tu Apni Hi Ore Khichh Naina De Khazaane Tere Lutt Ke Main Hona Rich

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
